作者：卜居。
Authors: Bocchu.
我把《健身环大冒险》安利给了从不玩游戏的我妈。
I gave "Fitness Ring Adventures" to my mother, who never played games.
她擅于做饭和洗衣服，爱好是唱歌、跳广场舞和唠叨我，人生的前五十五年几乎和电子游戏相绝缘。
She was good at cooking and washing, singing, plaza dancing, and nagging me. She was almost insulated from video games in the first 55 years of her life.
。
